Description:
You find a shop with many ancient objects that seem to be from nearby temples. When you approach a Naga comes out of the water and as he moves behind the counter he tells you:

"Hey hey, don't rush, I am peaceful and only interested in business, as you can see I have already explored all the waterfalls above and below the water, these are the best items I have found.

I want to make this shop famous, so I will offer you a fair trade."
DescriptionAction: It's time to do some shopping!
